<p style="text-align: justify;">Councillor Ali Thomas, Leader of NPT CBC, said: "I warmly congratulate Costain on being recognised in this way and I wish them every success in the national awards.  It is no surprise to me that they have won this accolade because this project has been an excellent example of working in partnership with and on behalf of the community.  This is one of the biggest projects this area has seen and Costain deserve a lot of credit for the way in which they have gone about it."</p>
