<p style="text-align: justify;">ESKTN’s Jonathan Abra will give details on the different funding mechanisms available and where they are appropriate, for both Costain’s internal supply chain and others invited by the ESKTN. The presentation will be ‘badged’ under the Company’s Engineering Tomorrow initiative.   </p>
