<p style="text-align: justify;">“ESKTN will give ideas and help companies with a pointer in the right direction towards gaining funding to support innovative solutions. There are various forms of funding out there set up for different situations, but not everyone knows some of the smaller funding routes that are available.”</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Tuesday’s event is intended to be the first in a series of webinars.</p>
