    <description><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: justify;">20 June 2012</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Costain (COST.LN), one of the UK’s leading engineering solutions providers, is pleased to announce that in Joint Venture (‘the JV’) with Skanska, it has been awarded a contract by Crossrail Limited worth approximately £40m in total.</p>
