    <description><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: justify;">5 July 2011</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Costain’s aim to contribute to the communities it works in, through ‘Costain Cares,’ is being demonstrated in Port Talbot, South Wales.</p>
